{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"大字报诗——一个落后分子的自白","authors":["北京大学","王国乡"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":5}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"大字报诗——一个落后分子的自白","type":"title"},{"text":"北京大学王国乡","type":"authors"},{"text":"（王国乡：北京大学中文系学生）","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"我知道，档案袋里领导给我作批语：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“该生在中学二年级，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"曾经不满团支部书记","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"因此是","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"对抗领导自由主义”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"三年前，我来北大","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"档案袋跟着屁股到这里","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"领导上一看这材料","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就把我划到最低级","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"从此我一直抬不起头","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"命中注定要受教育","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"隔几天","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就得找干部把思想来汇报","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要不然就是无纪律","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"见领导","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"只能作检讨","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不这样","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就是个人英雄主义","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我就象个媳妇，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"心中悲慼。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×　　×　　×","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有一次，我鼓起勇气，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"批评领导不民主","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有宗派主义。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这一来","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"帽子压了一大堆","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"对抗领导","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不满集体","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"把我吓得喘不过气。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×　　×　　×","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"那一年去实习","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"人家说","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“国防工业要保密，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你不能到那里去，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"因为你的政治质量‘低’”。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我想哭","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"眼泪咽到肚子里。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×　　×　　×","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"北京大学这么大，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我却没有个知巳，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"积极分子嫌我太落后，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不屑跟我在一起。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"班上老刘性情直","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"说话有些不客气","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"领导看他难掌握","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他和我划在同一“级”。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"心中闷","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"想找老刘来谈话","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"领导说：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“小集团活动要警惕”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我俩见面也不敢再搭理","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×　　×　　×","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一年级","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"学习马列主义","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"对斯大林的阶级斗争论","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我提出过问题","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"团支书警告我：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“这是立场不稳定，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"学习马列主义","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"怎么能怀疑！”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×　　×　　×","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"前年个","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"肃反时","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"老张说我有嫌疑","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"理由是：","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一贯对抗领导","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"搞小集体","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不满现实，还要攻击","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"马列主义","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这就是自发的反革命分子。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我听了，真着急。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"竭力争辩","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要他来证实","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"人家说","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“反革命分子！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这里没有你说话的权利”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"斗争会","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我受冤屈","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我的冤屈象白毛女","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我的诉说有谁理？？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"×　　×　　×","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"春天霹雷一声响","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"阳光普照在这里","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"如今我有了发言权，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"也把心里话提一提，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"批评家你别生气","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不要说我诬蔑社会主义","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"形象要有概括力","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"典型不等于作者自己","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"党也需要“乐府诗”。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","